{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<marquee>: The Marquee element","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard deprecated\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Deprecated:</strong> This feature is no longer recommended. Though some browsers might still support it, it may have already been removed from the relevant web standards, may be in the process of being dropped, or may only be kept for compatibility purposes. Avoid using it, and update existing code if possible; see the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">compatibility table</a> at the bottom of this page to guide your decision. Be aware that this feature may cease to work at any time.</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>&lt;marquee&gt;</code></strong> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML</a> element is used to insert a scrolling area of text. You can control what happens when the text reaches the edges of its content area using its attributes.</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">DOM interface</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMarqueeElement\"><code>HTMLMarqueeElement</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"Attributes","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"behavior\"><a id=\"attr-behavior\" href=\"#attr-behavior\"><b><code>behavior</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets how the text is scrolled within the marquee. Possible values are <code>scroll</code>, <code>slide</code> and <code>alternate</code>. If no value is specified, the default value is <code>scroll</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"bgcolor\"><a id=\"attr-bgcolor\" href=\"#attr-bgcolor\"><b><code>bgcolor</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets the background color through color name or hexadecimal value.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"direction\"><a id=\"attr-direction\" href=\"#attr-direction\"><b><code>direction</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets the direction of the scrolling within the marquee. Possible values are <code>left</code>, <code>right</code>, <code>up</code> and <code>down</code>. If no value is specified, the default value is <code>left</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"height\"><a id=\"attr-height\" href=\"#attr-height\"><b><code>height</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets the height in pixels or percentage value.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"hspace\"><a id=\"attr-hspace\" href=\"#attr-hspace\"><b><code>hspace</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets the horizontal margin</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"loop\"><a id=\"attr-loop\" href=\"#attr-loop\"><b><code>loop</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets the number of times the marquee will scroll. If no value is specified, the default value is −1, which means the marquee will scroll continuously.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"scrollamount\"><a id=\"attr-scrollamount\" href=\"#attr-scrollamount\"><b><code>scrollamount</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets the amount of scrolling at each interval in pixels. The default value is 6.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"scrolldelay\"><a id=\"attr-scrolldelay\" href=\"#attr-scrolldelay\"><b><code>scrolldelay</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets the interval between each scroll movement in milliseconds. The default value is 85. Note that any value smaller than 60 is ignored and the value 60 is used instead unless <code>truespeed</code> is specified.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"truespeed\"><a id=\"attr-truespeed\" href=\"#attr-truespeed\"><b><code>truespeed</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>By default, <code>scrolldelay</code> values lower than 60 are ignored. If <code>truespeed</code> is present, those values are not ignored.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"vspace\"><a id=\"attr-vspace\" href=\"#attr-vspace\"><b><code>vspace</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets the vertical margin in pixels or percentage value.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"width\"><a id=\"attr-width\" href=\"#attr-width\"><b><code>width</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Sets the width in pixels or percentage value.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"event_handlers","title":"Event handlers","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"onbounce\"><a id=\"attr-onbounce\" href=\"#attr-onbounce\"><b><code>onbounce</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fires when the marquee has reached the end of its scroll position. It can only fire when the behavior attribute is set to <code>alternate</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"onfinish\"><a id=\"attr-onfinish\" href=\"#attr-onfinish\"><b><code>onfinish</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fires when the marquee has finished the amount of scrolling that is set by the loop attribute. It can only fire when the loop attribute is set to some number that is greater than 0.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"onstart\"><a id=\"attr-onstart\" href=\"#attr-onstart\"><b><code>onstart</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Fires when the marquee starts scrolling.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"start\"><code>start()</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Starts scrolling of the marquee.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"stop\"><code>stop()</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Stops scrolling of the marquee.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This text will scroll from right to left<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">direction</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>up<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This text will scroll from bottom to top<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">direction</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>down<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>250<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>200<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">behavior</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>alternate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>solid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">behavior</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>alternate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> This text will bounce <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Examples sample\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/rendering.html#the-marquee-element-2","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.marquee"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.marquee","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMarqueeElement\"><code>HTMLMarqueeElement</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Attributes","id":"attributes"},{"text":"Event handlers","id":"event_handlers"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The <marquee> HTML element is used to insert a scrolling area of text. You can control what happens when the text reaches the edges of its content area using its attributes.","popularity":0.0118,"modified":"2022-09-14T07:57:28.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<marquee> : l'élément de fronton (obsolète)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<marquee>: マーキー要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"<marquee>：捲動元素（已過時）","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/html/element/marquee","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/html/element/marquee/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/b56483692fd247dd7c5f11af4233ad40bf19ac31","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML elements reference"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee","title":"<marquee>: The Marquee element"}],"pageTitle":"<marquee>: The Marquee element - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}